// ════════════════════ SHADER BACKDROP (budgeted Canvas2D dithered noise) ════════════════════
// Per spec: a budgeted procedural backdrop. Uses Canvas2D (universal) rather than raw WebGL
// for single-file safety; applies an ordered-dither noise field + radial vignette + slow drift.
// Auto-disables on prefers-reduced-motion or if frame budget is exceeded.
